    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, while the interior remains in showroom condition, retaining that signature new-car aroma and supple, unblemished leather. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians, with a complete paper trail included. From the flawless alloy wheels to the pristine engine bay, this car looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. It is, without question, the finest example currently available for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
